001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007import java.math.BigInteger;
008
009@HistoryLogProps(
010    opCode = 12,
011    displayName = "Pumping Resumed",
012    usedByTidepool = true
013)
014public class PumpingResumedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    private int insulinAmount;
017    
018    public PumpingResumedHistoryLog() {}
019    public PumpingResumedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int insulinAmount) {
020        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
021        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, insulinAmount);
022        this.insulinAmount = insulinAmount;
023        
024    }
025
026    public PumpingResumedHistoryLog(int insulinAmount) {
027        this(0, 0, insulinAmount);
028    }
029
030    public int typeId() {
031        return 12;
032    }
033
034    /**
035     * <table border="1">
036     * <caption>Parsed fields for PumpingResumedHistoryLog:</caption>
037     * <tr><td><code>insulinAmount</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
038     * </table>
039     */
040    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
041        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
042        this.cargo = raw;
043        parseBase(raw);
044        this.insulinAmount = Bytes.readShort(raw, 14);
045        
046    }
047
048    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int insulinAmount) {
049        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
050            new byte[]{12, 0},
051            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
052            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
053            new byte[4], // unknown -- uint32(100)
054            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(insulinAmount)));
055    }
056
057    /**
058     * @return the insulin amount at the time pumping was resumed (most likely the IOB, needs confirmation)
059     */
060    public int getInsulinAmount() {
061        return insulinAmount;
062    }
063    
064}
